  "body_html": "<i>Image illustrating ecg intervals</i><br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb093b.gif'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb093.gif'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://www.merckmanuals.com '  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb093b.gif'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER><br />Normal ECG Values are:<br /><ul><li>QRS complex is less than 0.12 secs</li><li>PR Interval 0.12 and 0.2 seconds</li><li>The QTc interval is less than 0.44 seconds</li><li>The RR interval is 0.6 to 1.0 seconds</li></ul></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodylinks\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodymedia\"></div>\n\n\n<div id=\"categorynum\">2</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategorynum\">2</div>\n\n<div id=\"categoryname\">Physiology</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategoryname\">Cardiovascular physiology</div>\n<div id=\"mybody\">\n\n<div id=\"body_content\">\n<i>Image illustrating ecg intervals</i><br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb093b.gif'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb093.gif'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://www.merckmanuals.com '  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb093b.gif'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER><br />Normal ECG Values are:<br /><ul><li>QRS complex is less than 0.12 secs</li><li>PR Interval 0.12 and 0.2 seconds</li><li>The QTc interval is less than 0.44 seconds</li><li>The RR interval is 0.6 to 1.0 seconds</li></ul></div>\n\n\n<BR><BR><br><br>",
